{"id": "1367469935894466621", "channel_id": "1367469935894466621", "type": 0, "author_id": "705407952575529022", "author_name": "water_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "戈雅：\n\n**請轉告逆活一世協助人員**\n\n根據空間本人的說明\n置入空間的指令卡皆為原始臨時複製\n理論上來說置入超維空間的幻夢詩篇與原本的幻夢詩篇是不同個體\n所以應該不會受到智識之理算力消耗+1的影響\n因此置入超維空間的幻夢詩篇還保留著算力消耗+1的影響是極為不合理的\n為了消除這等會讓人們對空間產生負面印象的案例，故特致此函\n若蒙應允，敬祈早賜佳音。先此致謝。\n\n\n察覺到奧爾拉主C夢還沒修聯盟會員\n蒯修 啟", "timestamp": "2025-05-01T11:57:19.080000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😲", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1367469936209035264", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-05-01-19-25-09-091_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 228517, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1367469935894466621/1367469936209035264/Screenshot_2025-05-01-19-25-09-091_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cc5f5f&is=69cb0ddf&hm=eba87b51bf510429b5e6c9dfa758f325ffded918eac44dca0d7af91bb47da22d&"}, {"id": "1367469936842113085", "filename": "Screenrecorder-2025-05-01-19-08-00-512.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 3053866, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1367469935894466621/1367469936842113085/Screenrecorder-2025-05-01-19-08-00-512.mp4?ex=69cc5f5f&is=69cb0ddf&hm=3368c022a2763d1677072ef23b76d8f7ae7a66e93487437b6a57e367d003bf05&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1367469935894466621", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」《無bug空間的逆襲 ～ 一度被稱為bug空間的我逆活一世，在維修公告拿出證明自己無bug的真本事 ～》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
